l\u0026#39;s newsletter that\u0026#39;s all about hosting gatherings big and small—without losing your cool. Got company? \u003ca href=\"https://food52.attn.tv/p/HBo/comeonover\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSign up here\u003c/a\u003e for her emails.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eThe most energy my husband and I can ever muster up for Valentine’s Day usually involves a dinner at Vinny’s, a casual Italian restaurant near us where the portions are huge and the prices are low. There’s never a wait, and we love it. This year, we might still go there—but I also want to pull a Leslie Knope and have my girlfriends over on the 13th, too. This calls for fondue.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n\n  \u003cdiv id=\"productCollectionRoot\"\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003eFrom Our Shop\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n  \u003ca data-sku-id=\"20048\" data-vendor-id=\"924\" data-vendor-name=\"Boska\" data-category-name=\"Specialty Cookware\" data-in-stock=\"true\" data-price=\"399.0\" data-ga-grid-item=\"slide: 2\" data-product-id=\"6550\" data-product-name=\"XL \u0026#34;Mr. Big\u0026#34; Fondue Pot\" data-url=\"/shop/products/6550-boska-mr-big-fondue-pot\" data-img=\"https://images.food52.com/qxFSBqFNBJAWkDK_pMHLkziVCMo=/520x520/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg\" data-price-range=\"$399\" data-ga-event=\"gridInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"From Our Shop\" data-ga-event-label=\"none\" data-ga-destination-url=\"/shop/products/6550-boska-mr-big-fondue-pot\" href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/6550-boska-mr-big-fondue-pot\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/C30Ex74eb7hyvu9h0HnoBR3h4vw=/520x520/filters:format(webp)/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg, https://images.food52.com/dQRXoEc1TZebAwcSHN5wQFMHGuk=/1040x1040/filters:format(webp)/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/qxFSBqFNBJAWkDK_pMHLkziVCMo=/520x520/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg, https://images.food52.com/SaMEikgG0ScFyRHV_QkpqOSeaFc=/1040x1040/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg 2x\" alt=\"XL \u0026#34;Mr. Big\u0026#34; Fondue Pot\" width=\"520\" height=\"520\" data-pin-media=\"https://images.food52.com/SaMEikgG0ScFyRHV_QkpqOSeaFc=/1040x1040/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg\" data-pin-url=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/6550-boska-mr-big-fondue-pot\" data-pin-description=\"XL \u0026#34;Mr. Big\u0026#34; Fondue Poton Food52\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/qxFSBqFNBJAWkDK_pMHLkziVCMo=/520x520/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg, https://images.food52.com/SaMEikgG0ScFyRHV_QkpqOSeaFc=/1040x1040/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://images.food52.com/SaMEikgG0ScFyRHV_QkpqOSeaFc=/1040x1040/da03d2b6-a51d-4a89-9970-d2f425e26913--2019-1010_boska_xl-mr-big-fondue-pot_1x1_rocky-luten_044.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003c/a\u003e\n\n    \n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n              \u003ch2\u003e1. Getting Cheesy\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eOur most popular \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/recipes/9534-traditional-fondue-fribourgeois-legendary-and-original\"\u003efondue recipe\u003c/a\u003e involves two kinds of cheese and about half a bottle of wine (plus Kirsch!). It also has the word “legendary” in the title—need I say more? It’s silky, never too gloopy, and perfect for a crowd.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n  \n\n\n\n              \u003ch2\u003e2. Do the Dip\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eMy friend Katherine, who owns an incredible dinner party shop called \u003ca href=\"https://bignightbk.com/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBig Night\u003c/a\u003e, taught me everything I know about what to pair with cheese fondue, from boiled potatoes to radishes to hunks of sourdough, and even grapes. Ask your friends to each bring a food they’d want to dunk in cheese. But also, we have \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/blog/24401-what-to-dip-in-cheese-fondue\"\u003eideas\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003ch2\u003e3. The ’70s Are Back\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/aDbh9a6MM1To88xtGS32W4bLS6w=/778x778/filters:format(webp)/a2a8efdb-bbee-4f68-8d87-44a48cbda741--2018-0809_boska_fondue-set-bianco_1x1_rocky-